The paper focuses on understanding and detecting fake reviews in app stores, which is a software engineering problem (cs.SE). It also involves analyzing data and developing a classifier, which falls under the categories of cybernetics (cs.CY), cryptography and security (cs.CR), information retrieval (cs.IR), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
